    "date": "2022-03-23T15:01:43Z",
    "text": "Enhancing Emergency and Retirement Savings Act of 2022\n\nThis bill permits penalty-free distributions, up to $1,000, from tax-exempt retirement plans for emergency personal expenses, limited to one distribution in a calendar year. The bill allows repayment to plans of such distributions over a three-year period."
